<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10145258>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Habitat and vegetative morphology of Lonchocarpus verticillatus A. Habitat in the Cauca River Canyon. B. Isolated tree in a pasture. C. Branch with whorled leaves and discolorous leaflets. D. Node of the branch and stipules (red arrows). E. Lenticellate trunk and yellowish inner bark. Photographs A–E: William Ariza." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10145258/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

